       I see your point.  The wording is very ambiguous.  Usually "remaining tasks" get run as part of the following call to `Next`.  Since the last item doesn't have a final call to `Next` we have to run those tasks before we return the final item.  I've updated the comment to just point out what is being tested and avoid making a comparison.




